1.title: United Axalon
1.plot: Let's go to Japan for a repaint of a toy that was released almost a decade prior and try to figure out why I love the mold so much.

2.title: RID 2015 Warrior Strongarm
2.plot: Going old school again for a random Transformer review, off the cuff and unscripted. Kicking off with something rather new, let's look at one of the new RID deluxes/warriors, my favorite of the first wave.

3.title: Robot Masters Star Saber
3.plot: Everyone's so hyped up for Masterpiece Star Saber, so it's a good time to look at the most recent version of the Victory leader - that wasn't a model kit.

4.title: RID 2015 Warrior Optimus Prime
4.plot: After my mistakes of my Strongarm review, I'm looking to get an RID toy right. So let's see how the new Optimus Prime turned out.

5.title: Prime Dark Energon Wheeljack
5.plot: Last week everyone told me what their favorite molds were, and someone's answer gave me an idea - So we'll look at one of the more recent oddities of redecoing.

6.title: Animated Blackout
6.plot: Cut short before it's time, the Animated toyline had a few leftovers that only came out in Japan. The one everyone wanted was Voyager Blackout, but was he worth all the demand and hype?

7.title: Beast Wars Telemocha BlackArachnia
7.plot: Filling in a request, I cover one of the most necessary repaints of all time. From Takara's anniversary Beast Wars line, it's the femme fatale, BlackArachnia.

8.title: Generations Warpath
8.plot: Finally getting the chance to talk about one of my favorite Transformer figures ever, and once again a favorite of mine only saw one retail release.

9.title: Beast Wars Neo Stampy
9.plot: Hey, it's as close to Easter as my video schedule allowed, okay? Just watch me talk about a plastic bunny a day late.

10.title: RID X-Brawn
10.plot: Answering the call to review my favorite of the RID Autobot Brothers.

11.title: Combiner Wars Dead End
11.plot: People wanted to see some Combiner Wars on Random Reviews, so they got it. And as long as we're going, it might as well be a new one, right?

12.title: Armada Nemesis Prime
12.plot: So people want to see a good Armada toy? Good, cause I've got one for you. Just one. And then there's no more.

13.title: Beast Machines BlackArachnia
13.plot: So a good Beast Machines toy now? Yeah, we can do that. And it's even a return for a previously reviewed character.

14.title: Machine Wars Starscream
14.plot: Remember Machine Wars? Me neither, but apparently I have this cool toy from it that was originally only going to be in Europe.

15.title: Universe Night Slash Cheetor
15.plot: The much needed repaint of an unneeded third Beast Machines Cheetor mold.

16.title: TFCC Thrustinator
16.plot: You got your Waspinator in my Thrust. You got your Thrust in my Waspinator.

17.title: R.I.D. Prowl
17.plot: Covering my second of the three Autobot Brothers from Robots In Disguise. ...the old one, not the new one.

18.title: Galaxy Force Inch Up
18.plot: Called Dirt Boss in another, English-speaking life, this monster truck was where my favorite toyline started for me.

19.title: Robot Masters Reverse Convoy
19.plot: One's a heroic warrior dedicated to protecting peace. The other is a tyrannical warmonger bent on conquest. But can they get along when living in - the same body?.

20.title: Botcon 2006 Darksyde Dinobot
20.plot: Welcome to the Darksyde - and no, that's not a May the 4th reference.

21.title: Energon Tow-Line
21.plot: The Energon Autobot who does it all himself. And kinda cheats his vehicle mode along the way.

22.title: Music Label Soundwave
22.plot: A Soundwave that plays actual music? Unpossible.

23.title: Titanium RID Optimus Prime
23.plot: Yes, there is such a thing as a good Titanium toy.

24.title: Combiner Wars Rook
24.plot: The newest member of the Protectobots is the one everyone's excited for - when has that ever happened?

25.title: Beast Wars Mutants Icebird
25.plot: A Transformer with no robot mode?

26.title: Prime Weaponizer Bumblebee
26.plot: But it's just a big gimmicky toy for little kids, right?

27.title: '07 Movie Fracture
27.plot: GOBOT ALERT. GOBO-oh - it's a Transformer AS a Gobot? Okay, false alarm, I'll allow it.

28.title: G1 Blitzwing
28.plot: My favorite G1 character of all time, but how does the toy hold up?

31.title: Combiner Wars Hot Spot
31.plot: A piece of my childhood is reborn.
